sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh/KServe<br/>Serving Pod
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant EvalPod as LM Evaluation Pod
    participant Driver as ta-lmes-driver<br/>18080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant Orchestrator as Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator Pod
    participant Detectors as Detector Services
    participant EHCtrl as EvalHub Controller
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/SQLite
    participant MLFlow as MLFlow Tracking

    Note over Client, TAS: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Payload Processing
    Client->>Router: POST /v1/models/predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>KRBP: Reencrypt<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBP->>TAS: Forward<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    MM->>KRBP: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>8443/TCP TLS (serving cert)
    KRBP->>TAS: Payload data<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS

    Note over Client, OCI: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution
    Client->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch notification
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>SA token
    Note over EvalPod: Init container copies<br/>driver binary
    EvalPod->>Driver: Start driver process
    Driver->>S3: Download assets (if offline)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, AWS IAM
    Note over Driver: Execute<br/>lm-evaluation-harness
    LMESCtrl->>Driver: GET /GetStatus<br/>18080/TCP HTTP (pod exec)
    Driver-->>LMESCtrl: Progress + status
    Driver->>OCI: Upload results (if configured)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over GORCHCtrl, Detectors: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Discovery
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>SA token
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List Services by label<br/>SA token
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMaps<br/>(orchestrator config)
    Client->>Router: Request to Orchestrator<br/>HTTPS
    Router->>Orchestrator: Forward via kube-rbac-proxy
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Check content safety<br/>HTTPS/HTTP
    Orchestrator->>MM: Forward to InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/HTTP

    Note over EHCtrl, MLFlow: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation and Monitoring
    Client->>Router: API request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Router->>EvalHub: Reencrypt<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    Note over EvalHub: SAR + X-Tenant scoping
    EvalHub->>DB: Query/Store data<br/>5432/TCP
    EvalHub->>MLFlow: Experiment tracking<br/>HTTPS, projected SA token
    EHCtrl->>EvalHub: Job failure events<br/>POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
